lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Jelena Ostapenko of Latvia beat qualifier Daniela Hantuchova of Slovakia 6-1, 6-1 to advance to the second round of the Katowice Open on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Ostapenko, Cornet, Giorgi Make 2nd Round of Katowice Open
headline.main: Ostapenko, Cornet, Giorgi Make 2nd Round of Katowice Open
